  <brief_title>Prevention of Postoperative Nausea and Vomiting (PONV) by Acupressure</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prevention of PONV by Acupressure. A Study of the Effect of a Recently Generated Danish Bracelet Vital-Band(R) Which Stimulates the Acupressure Point P6</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Herlev Hospital</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Herlev Hospital</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether stimulation to the akupressurpoint P6 with
      a recently developed bracelet are effective preventing postoperative nausea and vomiting
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
