  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Female,

          -  Non-smoker,

          -  &gt;18 years,

          -  ASA 1 or 2,

          -  Signed patient information,

          -  IV-anaestesia.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Male,

          -  Smoker,

          -  ASA 3 or 4,

          -  Pregnancy,

          -  Nausea and vomiting within the last 24 h before operation,

          -  Diabetes,

          -  Carpaltunnel syndrome,

          -  Lymphedema of arms,

          -  Eczema of forearm,

          -  Patients who earlier has undergone removal of lymph nodes in the armpits,

          -  Inhalation anaestesia.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
